                            CONTACT THE COMMITTEE

         Mail delivery to the U.S. House of Representatives has been
      temporarily suspended.  It is best to contact the Committee in the
                               following ways:

   Phone: (202) 225-3625
   Fax: (202) 225-2610
   E-Mail: contact.waysandmeans@mail.house.gov

   The Committee on Ways and Means welcomes your comments or questions
   about the Committee's Web site.  You may contact the Committee by email
   at: webmaster.waysandmeans@mail.house.gov.

   NOTE:  To locate and email your Member of Congress, go to the "Write
   Your Rep" site at   http://www.house.gov/writerep.  Thank you.

